Highlights of 2022 series starting off with this insane experience outside my comfort zone, that I loved so much I want to repeat yearly. Connecting fully with nature, your thoughts, your body, mind and soul. How? By silencing everything else, by restricting yourself from things like sugar, alcohol, caffeine, television, phones (and in this case meat, lactose and gluten!) oh and just add 6 mountain climbs (5 hours a day) in 8 days + all the fun stuff like yoga, workouts and spa treatments to be able to do it all again the following day. HIGHLY RECOMMEND a bi-yearly or yearly reset 🤍
